Free Play Days events

   Access full games across a variety of genres for free every month on
   select weekends. Availability period for each game may vary.

   No active Free Play Day events at this time. Check back soon.

   1. Network claim: Independent IHS Markit study, June/July 2017. Tested
   on Xbox One S v. PlayStation 4 Pro on top 5 selling games with
   matchmaking; results may vary, not an endorsement.
   Visit www.xbox.com/betternetwork.

   2. Requirements and available features vary across consoles;
   multiplayer between Xbox One and Xbox 360 supported for select titles.
   Download required. Visit www.xbox.com/backcompat.

   3. Active Gold membership required to play free games you’ve redeemed.
   Restrictions Apply.

   4. Savings based on retail value of game.

   5. For paid Gold members only. On Xbox One, active Gold membership
   required to play free games you’ve redeemed. Restrictions Apply.
   Requirements and available features vary across consoles; Multiplayer
   between Xbox One and Xbox 360 not supported. See www.xbox.com/live

   After each Free Play Days period ends, you must buy the game(s) to
   continue playing, and to continue using any add-ons or items purchased
   for the game(s). Achievements earned carry over for purchased game(s).
